.idea/**/sqlDataSources.xml
.idea/**/dynamic.xml
.idea/**/uiDesigner.xml
.idea/**/dbnavigator.xml

## Gradle
.idea/**/gradle.xml
.idea/**/libraries

## Gradle and Maven with auto-import; skip version catalog file
!gradle/libs.versions.toml

## CMake
cmake-build-*/

## File-based project format
*.iws

